Dear Kevin, you may no longer be with us in body, but your love, wisdom, and laughter remain with us for the rest of our lives. You are dearly missed and forever cherished. As we come together for this fundraiser, we find comfort in knowing that our love for Kevin Huapaya & our dedication to carrying forward his legacy is stronger than ever. This event is not just a fundraiser; it is a celebration of a life well-lived, a life that continues to inspire and touch our lives even in his absence. We invite you to join us as we cherish the memories we had together with Kevin. The funds raised during this event will be directly going to the loving Huapaya family. We all miss you so much, Long Live Kevin Martin Huapaya Vasquez, forever in our hearts 🕊️🙏🏽🤍

Christmas ‘23 holiday card 💌🎄

5 days Away from 2024 🥂 

We hope you had a fantastic Christmas filled with joy and love! As we gear up for the final countdown to 2024, we wanted to express our gratitude for your unwavering support over the years. 

To show our appreciation, we’re thrilled to present a promo code to this years NYE! 

🚨 Enter the promo code LAVIEWHARF24 at checkout to enjoy a 10% discount on your ticket purchase 🚨 

There are just a few days left to grab your ticket so be sure to purchase before they are gone!

Thank you for being an integral part of our community and always making our events truly special! We look forward to celebrating the start of 2024 with you at La Vie DC this Sunday.
